</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Erm...</span><hr size=1> See, this is why I hold very, very few opinions.  They are easier to ignore than facts (assuming you aren't very good at ignoring facts).  This argument will not get anywhere.  Everyone is too busy using opinions as facts to help rationalize his/her view.<br>
<br>
*sighs*<br>
